{"tid":248150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼南海軍演 中國製防空炮故障誤炸死4兵","createTime":"2017-05-18T10:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T11:40:32.000Z","uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edb3af72bb5c2e7b59410c59a3159c67a6eaea3b","tid":248150,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"印尼南海軍演 華製防空炮故障誤炸死4兵<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170518/mobile/bkncn-20170518153834651-0518_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170518%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20170518153834651-0518_05011_001.html&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b09ad8bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170518/mobile/bkncn-20170518153834651-0518_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f602b9f68ce035574b7cf38bd157aaee55ad4900","tid":248150,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"trojan horse"},{"pid":"da891a060b009f15be692c71814c670de0d9c842","tid":248150,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf79d133a9c38e642bc0c035291177018b220d1","tid":248150,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"中國製的「巨弓」（Giant Bow）火炮射擊目標靶時發生故障，誤射另一個方向，多名士兵走避不及遭殃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6ab104d70b5da118490e4941ce395c151d151b","tid":248150,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddb990926816f9e61de2be9fe918f99679e02fa","tid":248150,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"全自動化"},{"pid":"e8b7af07dceb85df26d3f30d585772f67ded7477","tid":248150,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:51:10.000Z","msg":"印尼軍演 中國製火炮失控致4死8傷 <br />\n<br />\n5月18日，印尼軍隊在納土納群島（Natuna Islands）演習 時，因使用的一台中國製防空火炮突然失控，使得炮彈射向自家官兵，造成4人死亡，8人 受傷，其中4人重傷。 <br />\n<br />\n據《雅加達郵報》（Jakarta Post）報導，事件發生在納土納群島（Natuna Islands）基 地，印尼軍方快速打擊部隊舉行軍事演習，採用中國製的「巨弓」（Giant Bow）火砲射 擊標靶時失控，多名士兵走避不及遭殃。 <br />\n<br />\n印尼軍方發言人阿爾法雷特（Alfret Denny Tuejeh）表示，這場演習是例行性的軍事演 習。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，肇事的雙炮管防空炮是印尼軍方於2003年向中共購買，當局正調查事故原因。 納土納群島位於馬來半島和婆羅洲島之間，之前因印尼的經濟海域和中國主張的南海主權 範圍局部重疊，令雙方關係一度緊張。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/5/18/n9156621.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F17%2F5%2F18%2Fn9156621.htm&d=ke1AtGtnimFyOKizm7Qk%2BW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=70075021\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/5/18/n9156621.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d34f69477fa711e7c519811fafaee80fcce56643","tid":248150,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb77f017a79b7ffbc3fe24d8a37b440ba90fa57","tid":248150,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"印尼想用中國制造嘅炮響南海軍演意圖對付中國?<br />\n聽起上黎鬼鬼地! 一定被hack!?"},{"pid":"624df5ac5d6f8f6baffb2da4bd37187eebe2f15d","tid":248150,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"古惑的鎗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68f15fcd1f8cffb656eee0264d2d494c3004953","tid":248150,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T11: